  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Renovation Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Ruby Reno Pte. Ltd. is a fast-growing renovation company in Singapore, specialising in residential and commercial renovation works. We are looking for a driven and experienced <strong>Renovation Sales Executive</strong> to join our dynamic team.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Source, manage, and close renovation sales leads</p></li><li><p>Conduct site visits, understand client requirements, and propose suitable renovation solutions</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations, pricing, and cost breakdowns</p></li><li><p>Negotiate contracts and pricing with clients professionally</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with project and operations teams to ensure smooth project execution</p></li><li><p>Actively participate in marketing efforts, including social media and online platforms</p></li><li><p>Maintain strong relationships with clients to encourage repeat business and referrals</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Minimum 3 years of experience</strong> in renovation sales and project management</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of renovation works, materials, and costing</p></li><li><p>Able to handle <strong>pricing, quotation preparation, and negotiations</strong> independently</p></li><li><p>Proficient in <strong>marketing and social media platforms</strong> (Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, results-driven, and good interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p><strong>Own car preferred</strong> (for site visits and client meetings)</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>High commission structure</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Attractive bonuses</strong> (more competitive than other companies)</p></li><li><p>Supportive team and growth opportunities</p></li><li><p>Flexible and performance-driven work environment</p></li></ul>",
